A '''hunting tournament''' is a live kill competition where individuals or teams try to kill the largest animal for [[hunting|sport]].  There are many types of hunting tournaments and they are all scored differently.  Some organizations that endorse hunting tournaments are the [[National Rifle Association]] and [[Safari Club International]].

